end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9296799338988393, \"rank\": 0.06072136662945411, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Chen Yiwen and Chang Yani also advanced to the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 3-meter springboard final on Friday.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yiwen\", \"score\": 0.9999955748669574, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Yiwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yiwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yiwen\"}, {\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chang_Yani\", \"score\": 0.999957464354512, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chang Yani\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chang_Yani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chang_Yani\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In sports climbing, China's Wu Peng won silver in the men's speed big final, clocking a time of 4.77 seconds.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1592, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9296799338988393, \"rank\": 0.06072136662945411, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wu_Peng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.383353801685686e-20, \"text\": \"Wu Peng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wu_Peng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wu_Peng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Veddriq Leonardo of Indonesia won the g