n's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9585013195960094, \"rank\": 0.029567652109804644, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team China also advanced to the final of the men's 4x100 metee relay.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2359, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9666453907316967e-23, \"text\": \"Team China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pakistan's Arshad Nadeem won the Olympic men's javelin title on Thursday, earning his country its first individual gold medal at a Summer Games.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999731646265961, \"rank\": 2.6767167201922666e-05, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2441, \"end\": 2454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arshad Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Americans Grant Holloway and Daniel Roberts won gold and silver, respectively, in the 110-meter hurdles, with Jamaica\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Rasheed Broadbell taking bronze.\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2730, \"