 with 29 gold medals and 73 total medals, and Australia with 18 gold medals and 45 total medals.\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3182, \"end\": 3187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9296799338988393, \"rank\": 0.06072136662945411, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 3233, \"end\": 3242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999993919547735, \"rank\": 4.120580559454947e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more, check out our exclusive content onCGTN Nowand subscribe to our weekly newsletter,The China Report.\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3380, \"end\": 3392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Report\", \"score\": 0.9999999811147975, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Report\", \"types\": [\"Q737498\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Report\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Report\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": []}]}"